Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分开了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为邪恶帝皇多恶达\N支配了这座山的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连彩虹的颜色也变成了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、火美子和武一郎师傅\N一边与多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于上了第三界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.22,0:01:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本第三界层是由\N支配寒冷的极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和支配炎热的灼热之盾\N令这世界的气温刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.80,0:02:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多恶达用灼热之剑\N换了极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令第三界层变成了一个\N热得不得了的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了令这世界恢复原来气温\N便一定要找到极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了找极寒之剑\N和师傅他们分开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来到了第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.22,0:02:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里火龙告诉我\N要到野野谷去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六话\N悲恋,极光传说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我技术不错吧\N嗨,野野谷还有很远吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很没精神呢\N好,在到达之前玩接尾句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接尾句（接屁股）?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么?\N只要用词语来玩游戏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.58,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂吗?算了\N那休息一下吧,有点累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊\N不快点找到极寒之剑不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是\N但是只是休息一会可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而令人更冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这处真是个阴森可怕的地方\N渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.62,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山是连村内的人\N也未去过的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里是非常神圣的地方\N进入这里的人都会中邪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是的\N你想用那些话来吓我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然变得精神了\N不如出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极光?这便是极光吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有照相机便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已看惯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种色的极光是第一次见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?是雾吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也看不见呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.73,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,玩那个吧\N叫接尾句的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,那么,首先是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪(YUKII)的KI\N你要说出用KI开头的词语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KI吗?那么…啄木鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是KI吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KI,KI,KI…\N不要催我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,前面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓紧我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,它追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙太冷冬眠了吗?\N起来啊!小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难缠的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,再快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了,已不能再加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你想对我们怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要吃的话\N我们也完全不好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,竟当我是傻瓜\N我已生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!去吧!小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊!快离开雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋,喷火吧,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你不是百人仙人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里?\N而且变得很细小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识百人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是在第三界层见过面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.51,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三界层?那便是真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千人仙人\N是百人仙人的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?所以才这么像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.81,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫西蒙\N是守护我的善良生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?原来是这样\N吓了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.72,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.98,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙是神圣的生物\N随便碰的会受到天罚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.77,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是西蒙\N这附近一带也是在守护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以便没有人敢接近这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千人仙人\N请问野野谷在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里便是野野谷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?那么这里会有\N极寒之剑的线索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,快点去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚才扭伤了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走到这里\N应该没什么大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你从刚才起\N便一直在忍着吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从火美子那拿了万能药来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,涂点药吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.40,0:09:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说救世主在创界山出现了\N难道是这个少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N这药的效力令人难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢这个样子回来\N你知不知丑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次一定会令渡知道\N什么是无用的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,但这次再失败的话\N别忘了你将失去翻身之地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次会打起精神作战的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢\N完全没有像样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?千人仙人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢\N好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,不可以摸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!千人仙人去了哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说些话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由能答我吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.33,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,它不是想吓我\N而是想和我玩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,不要啊,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会和人亲近的西蒙也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年果然是真正的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千人仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,我告诉你\N有关亚撒姆和胡娜拉的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚撒姆和胡娜拉的传说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千人仙人,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很遥远的昔日,神的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看,那棵很大的树下有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他便是亚撒姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚撒姆原来是秋天和冬天的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.71,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而春天和夏天的神\N是位叫胡娜拉的女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们二人犯了一个\N不能回头的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相爱的人永不分离\N也许是很自然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.20,0:12:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是秋天和冬天的神\N与春天和夏天的神在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会令季节转换消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,他们相爱\N本来便是不容许的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算因他们的关系\N令其他人受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也绝不分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时爱的女神处罚了他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受心替之矢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉变成了石像\N被困到了第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心被抽空的亚撒姆很伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太伤心的关系\N令亚撒姆也变成了石像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱之女神也是这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.76,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以便只容许他们\N一千年相聚一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一千年,亚撒姆像\N都会架起一道光之桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.51,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直通往第四界层的那道光\N亚撒姆和胡娜拉便重聚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个便是亚撒姆和胡娜拉的传说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极寒之剑便在胡娜拉像手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么胡娜拉像在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡娜拉像\N为了追寻亚撒姆像的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四界层中四处游走不定\N没有人知道她在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.88,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千年一度之日快来到了\N那个极光便是先兆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快亚撒姆和胡娜拉便相聚\N也许那时便是机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你不要有事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,洞穴内比较凉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡就像是我儿子一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.96,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一人在踏上危险的旅程时\N在下享乐是武士之耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,你原来是渡的父亲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.05,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,和你说话令我很累\N你走开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来祈求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.06,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以抱着玩的心情啊\N要诚心诚意地祈求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样渡才能安然回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,谁也不明白我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残酷大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怕什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的家伙\N还可以迷惘吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗,古拿玛\N再次失败是不可饶恕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真失败的话…\N你便没有命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…\N我发现了有好东西吃的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下担心渡,没有食欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊?\N在这屋内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要第一\N是在下先啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师! 什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的家伙,好了,去吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?没有食物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,有点不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!是"巴BQ"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,斩不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!古拿玛,来帮手啊\N喂!古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.07,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!\N难道古拿玛那家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你竟敢瞒骗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么千人仙人,我们出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那极光前进\N一定会有些什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢,呆在这里想的话\N什么也找不到,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是东杰何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得\N总算不是无用的反抗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你已引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,竟敢这样说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了,那些冰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流下来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你便明白\N什么是无用的反抗了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在做无用的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的反抗不是无用的\N去吧!西蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,已不可饶恕了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样便用魔神决胜负吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙多龙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[妙多龙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会让你们逃出这个山谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,西蒙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的反抗!无用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!\N好了,最后一击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!奇怪珠攻击!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!是机会了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.13,0:20:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!可恶的龙神丸\N今天一定要和你做个了断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的龙神丸\N我要把你打得稀烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无用的反抗呢,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我令你死得痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再阻碍我了\N那么我先收拾你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么家伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掷回去吧!龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.57,0:21:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是无用的反抗啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.01,0:21:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙一定可以帮到你们\N带它去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,千人仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,出发吧,西蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心了!


